{"_id":"2bq5iEZewkgRCYrN","name":"Ancestral Predator Shield Adjustment","type":"equipment","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/shields/specific-shields/nethysian-bulwark.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Stitched onto a leather face, painted, or lacquered on, you have created an image on the face of your shield that evokes an ancient fear from a specific group. Choose a type of creature that isn't typically mindless such as aberration, animal, astral, dragon, elemental, ethereal, fey, fiend, giant, humanoid, or monitor. You etch an image of an ancient foe for that type of creature on the face of your shield, and can brandish it to make yourself more intimidating. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to all Intimidation checks made against creatures of the chosen type while you're wielding this shield. You may choose undead as your type, but consider that many undead are mindless and immune to all mental effects, including Intimidation.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["adjustment"],"rarity":"uncommon","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[{"key":"FlatModifier","label":"Ancestral Predator","selector":"intimidation","predicate":{"all":["ancestral-predator"]},"type":"circumstance","value":1}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":20}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","invested":null,"handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":"","negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/adventuring_gear.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"applied-to-shield"},"level":{"value":3}},"ownership":{"default":0,"4mqS4QLqshw8WhsN":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668741178122,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"name":"Bottled Firefly Swarm, True","type":"consumable","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/alchemical-items/alchemical-poisons/giant-wasp-venom.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Activate&nbsp;</strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">f&nbsp;</span>envision;&nbsp;<strong>Trigger&nbsp;</strong>An enemy targets you with an attack.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>This bottle emits a buzzing sound that can only be heard if you hold it up to your ear. When you activate the bottle, a swarm of insects is released into the attacker's face. The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.XgEqL1kFApUbl5Z2]{Blinded} until the end of their turn and must attempt a flat check as normal to determine if the attack misses due to the target being hidden.</p>\n<p>The target is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TkIyaNPgTZFBCCuh]{Dazzled} for 1 minute.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["conjuration","magical","talisman"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":1600}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/other-consumables.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"affixed-to-a-shield"},"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoUse":true,"autoDestroy":true},"spell":null,"level":{"value":16},"consumableType":{"value":"talisman"},"charges":{"value":0,"max":0,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"autoUse":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true},"autoDestroy":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4da2MjIv6iDbKV1P"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668398310699,"modifiedTime":1668402795086,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"_id":"3Nb3VtGM6Fn8cL7A","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd":3},"schemaVersion":13}
{"name":"Adamantine Flake","type":"consumable","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/adventuring-gear/flint-and-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Activate&nbsp;</strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">f&nbsp;</span>envision;&nbsp;<strong>Trigger&nbsp;</strong>You use the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.jM72TjJ965jocBV8]{Shield Block} reaction.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>This tiny fleck of adamantine can impart some of its incredible hardness to the shield it is attached to. When activated, it grants the attached shield a +2 item bonus to Hardness for 1 minute.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["magical","talisman","transmutation"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":8}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/other-consumables.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"affixed-to-a-shield"},"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoUse":true,"autoDestroy":true},"spell":null,"level":{"value":3},"consumableType":{"value":"talisman"},"charges":{"value":0,"max":0,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"autoUse":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true},"autoDestroy":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4da2MjIv6iDbKV1P"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668398310699,"modifiedTime":1668741162009,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"_id":"4da2MjIv6iDbKV1P","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd":3},"schemaVersion":13}
{"name":"Tree Sap","type":"consumable","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/alchemical-items/alchemical-elixirs/mana-rattler-liniment.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Activate&nbsp;</strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">f </span>command</p>\n<hr>\n<p>This waxed pouch contains thick tree sap. When activated, the face of your shield becomes incredibly sticky. For 1 round the shield gains the grapple trait.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["magical","talisman","transmutation"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":8}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/other-consumables.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"affixed-to-a-shield"},"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoUse":true,"autoDestroy":true},"spell":null,"level":{"value":3},"consumableType":{"value":"talisman"},"charges":{"value":0,"max":0,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"autoUse":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true},"autoDestroy":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4da2MjIv6iDbKV1P"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTi