{"name":"Heartstone","type":"consumable","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/consumables/ammunition/backpack-catapult-stone.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Activate </strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> command</p>\n<hr>\n<p>This small dense stone is wrapped in wire. When activated, it spreads across the face of your shield and up the arm that wields it, protecting it and its wearer for as long as the stone holds up aginst attack. Your shield gains 5d6 + 10 temporary Hit Points and you gain half that amount.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["magical","talisman","transmutation"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":160}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/other-consumables.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"affixed-to-a-shield"},"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoUse":true,"autoDestroy":true},"spell":null,"level":{"value":10},"consumableType":{"value":"talisman"},"charges":{"value":0,"max":0,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"autoUse":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true},"autoDestroy":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4da2MjIv6iDbKV1P"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668398310699,"modifiedTime":1668402804000,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"_id":"YxUl7f6Dj2zYbh3v","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd":3},"schemaVersion":13}
{"name":"Bottled Firefly Swarm, Major","type":"consumable","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/alchemical-items/alchemical-poisons/giant-wasp-venom.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Activate&nbsp;</strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">f&nbsp;</span>envision;&nbsp;<strong>Trigger&nbsp;</strong>An enemy targets you with an attack.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>This bottle emits a buzzing sound that can only be heard if you hold it up to your ear. When you activate the bottle, a swarm of insects is released into the attacker's face. The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TkIyaNPgTZFBCCuh]{Dazzled} until the end of their turn and must attempt a flat check as normal to determine if the attack misses due to concealment.</p>\n<p>The creature must also pass a DC 25 Fortitude save or be dazzled for 1 minute.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["conjuration","magical","talisman"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":100}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/other-consumables.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"affixed-to-a-shield"},"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoUse":true,"autoDestroy":true},"spell":null,"level":{"value":8},"consumableType":{"value":"talisman"},"charges":{"value":0,"max":0,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"autoUse":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true},"autoDestroy":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4da2MjIv6iDbKV1P"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668398310699,"modifiedTime":1668402773404,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"_id":"a6eKLqyYujrwNmSz","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd":3},"schemaVersion":13}
{"name":"Prismatic Crystal","type":"consumable","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/spells/prismatic-shield.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Activate&nbsp;</strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">f&nbsp;</span>envision;&nbsp;<strong>Trigger&nbsp;</strong>You are targeted by, or in the area of an effect that deals acid, cold, electricity, fire, poison, or sonic damage.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>A small crystal that refracts light into its constituent colors, wrapped in a leather cord that can be tied to your shield. When activated, for 1 minute your shield transforms into an elemental version of the triggering damage type. During this effect, you may use your @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.jM72TjJ965jocBV8]{Shield Block} reaction when you would take damage from the triggering damage type in addition to physical damage, and your shield is immune to the triggering damage type.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["magical","talisman","transmutation"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":12}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/other-consumables.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"affixed-to-a-shield"},"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoUse":true,"autoDestroy":true},"spell":null,"level":{"value":4},"consumableType":{"value":"talisman"},"charges":{"value":0,"max":0,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"autoUse":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true},"autoDestroy":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4da2MjIv6iDbKV1P"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668398310699,"modifiedTime":1668402872847,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"_id":"cOSMa6SvLAnYbQC7","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd":3},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"hndgv2DOMiuOWz2H","name":"Barbed Edges Shield Adjustment","type":"equipment","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/adventuring-gear/glass-cutter.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You have added barbs around the edge of your shield's face that are particularly effective when used against creatures in very tight quarters. When you use the @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.SkZAQRkLLkmBQNB9]{Escape} action against a creature to remove the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.kWc1fhmv9LBiTuei]{Grabbed}, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.eIcWbB5o3pP6OIMe]{Immobilized}, or @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.VcDeM8A5oI6VqhbM]{Restrained} condition and you do not roll a critical failure on the check, you also deal [[/r 2d6]] slashing damage to the creature.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["adjustment"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":40}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","invested":null,"handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":"","negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/adventuring_gear.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"applied-to-shield"},"level":{"value":5}},"ownership":{"default":0,"4mqS4QLqshw8WhsN":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668741254509,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"kxFxItXqcfFlhtqM","name":"Coat of Arms Shield Adjustment","type":"equipment","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/shields/specific-shields/medusas-scream.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Stitched onto a leather face, painted, or lacquered on, a coat of arms can mean a great deal depending on whom you're addressing. It can lend weight to your words, the deals you make, and even the insults you throw. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Diplomacy checks while you are wielding the shield, as long as the coat of arms represents a faction that would be feared or respected by the target of the check, at the GM's discretion.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["adjustment","visual"],"rarity":"uncommon","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[{"key":"FlatModifier","label":"Coat of Arms","selector":"diplomacy","predicate":{"all":["coat-of-arms"]},"type":"circumstance","value":1}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":20}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","invested":null,"handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":"","negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/adventuring_gear.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"applied-to-shield"},"level":{"value":3}},"ownership":{"default":0,"4mqS4QLqshw8WhsN":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668741326082,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"name":"Adamantine Flake, True","type":"consumable","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/adventuring-gear/flint-and-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Activate&nbsp;</strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">f&nbsp;</span>envision;&nbsp;<strong>Trigger&nbsp;</strong>You use the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.jM72TjJ965jocBV8]{Shield Block} reaction.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>This tiny fleck of adamantine can impart some of its incredible hardness to the shield it is attached to. When activated, it grants the attached shield a +14 item bonus to Hardness for 1 minute.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["magical","talisman","transmutation"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":1600}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/other-consumables.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"affixed-to-a-shield"},"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoUse":true,"autoDestroy":true},"spell":null,"level":{"value":18},"consumableType":{"value":"talisman"},"charges":{"value":0,"max":0,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"autoUse":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true},"autoDestroy":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4da2MjIv6iDbKV1P"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668398310699,"modifiedTime":1668402699672,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"_id":"sv4vA03QDB5HTC3X","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd":3},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"v6TJPCrWPXbzfwbI","name":"Shield Strap Shield Adjustment","type":"equipment","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/worn-items/other-worn-items/bellflower-toolbelt.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Usage</strong> applied to a light or medium shield</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You have attached a leather or chain strap to your shield that you can loop over your forearm or a shoulder. When you&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">@Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.wQYmDStjdjn0I26t]{Release}</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">&nbsp;your shield it doesn't fall to the ground and is considered to be worn. You may draw it as normal after Releasing it. The strap has a quick release, allowing you to still use actions and reactions that require throwing your shield, such as Interrupting Shield, but reattaching the strap is a three-action activity with the manipulate trait.</span></p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["adjustment"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":1}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","invested":null,"handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":"","negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/adventuring_gear.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"applied-to-shield"},"level":{"value":1}},"ownership":{"default":0,"4mqS4QLqshw8WhsN":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668741341313,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"name":"Bottled Firefly Swarm","type":"consumable","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/alchemical-items/alchemical-poisons/giant-wasp-venom.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Activate&nbsp;</strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">f&nbsp;</span>envision;&nbsp;<strong>Trigger&nbsp;</strong>An enemy targets you with an attack.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>This bottle emits a buzzing sound that can only be heard if you hold it up to your ear. When you activate the bottle, a swarm of insects is released into the attacker's face. The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TkIyaNPgTZFBCCuh]{Dazzled} for the triggering attack and must attempt a flat check as normal to determine if the attack misses due to concealment.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["conjuration","magical","talisman"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":2}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/other-consumables.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"affixed-to-a-shield"},"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoUse":true,"autoDestroy":true},"spell":null,"level":{"value":1},"consumableType":{"value":"talisman"},"charges":{"value":0,"max":0,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"autoUse":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true},"autoDestroy":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4da2MjIv6iDbKV1P"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668398310699,"modifiedTime":1668402736779,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"_id":"vdX2bbcB0Hu1zxPg","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd":3},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"w2pZ4j6qczs1Dky4","name":"Shield Harness Shield Adjustment","type":"equipment","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/worn-items/other-worn-items/inexplicable-apparatus.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Usage</strong> applied to a medium or heavy shield</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your shield has been modified so that you can harness it firmly to your back when you are not actively wielding it. When you are wearing your shield instead of wielding it, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC against attacks made against you if you are considered flat-footed against the attack because you are flanked by another enemy. If you are hit by such an attack, you take the damage as normal. The shield also takes the damage but reduces it by its Hardness. If the shield is broken or destroyed, you no longer receive this benefit.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["adjustment"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":105}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","invested":null,"handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":"","negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/adventuring_gear.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"applied-to-shield"},"level":{"value":7}},"ownership":{"default":0,"4mqS4QLqshw8WhsN":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668741336824,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"name":"Tree Sap, Greater","type":"consumable","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/alchemical-items/alchemical-elixirs/mana-rattler-liniment.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Activate&nbsp;</strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">f </span>command</p>\n<hr>\n<p>This waxed pouch contains thick tree sap. When activated, the face of your shield becomes incredibly sticky. For 1 minute the shield gains the grapple trait.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["magical","talisman","transmutation"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":40}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn"},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/other-consumables.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"affixed-to-a-shield"},"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoUse":true,"autoDestroy":true},"spell":null,"level":{"value":6},"consumableType":{"value":"talisman"},"charges":{"value":0,"max":0,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"autoUse":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true},"autoDestroy":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4da2MjIv6iDbKV1P"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668398310699,"modifiedTime":1668402047171,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"_id":"wX2st2rabk5deiMJ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd":3},"schemaVersion":13}
{"name":"Venom Pouch, Greater","type":"consumable","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/alchemical-items/alchemical-poisons/yellow-musk-vial.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Activate&nbsp;</strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">f&nbsp;</span>envision;&nbsp;<strong>Trigger&nbsp;</strong>You use @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.jM72TjJ965jocBV8]{Shield Block} against an unarmed melee Strike or a Strike made by a non-reach melee weapon.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>This small brown pouch contains the venom of a poisonous creature. When activated, the triggering creature must attempt a Fortitude save against DC 27. On a failed save, the creature takes 4d6 persistent poison damage.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["magical","necromancy","talisman"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":160}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/other-consumables.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"affixed-to-a-shield"},"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoUse":true,"autoDestroy":true},"spell":null,"level":{"value":10},"consumableType":{"value":"talisman"},"charges":{"value":0,"max":0,"_deprecated":true},"consume":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"autoUse":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true},"autoDestroy":{"value":true,"_deprecated":true}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4da2MjIv6iDbKV1P"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668398310699,"modifiedTime":1668402988889,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"_id":"wqoDz2gzTjBsctQo","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd":3},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"y5mrfJGxewRcQxJM","name":"Shield Sheath Shield Adjustment","type":"equipment","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/adventuring-gear/sheath.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You have added a bracket or sheath to your shield that allows you to stow your weapon. A weapon sheath can contain a single one-handed weapon whose bulk cannot exceed the bulk of the shield. When you draw your shield, if you have a free hand and there is a weapon in the shield's weapon sheath, you may draw that weapon with the same interact action you use to draw the shield. Stowing a weapon in the sheath requires a single Interact action.</p>\n<p>This adjustment cannot be applied to a shield with the accessible trait.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["adjustment"],"rarity":"common","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":1}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","invested":null,"handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":"","negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/adventuring_gear.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"applied-to-shield"},"level":{"value":1}},"ownership":{"default":0,"4mqS4QLqshw8WhsN":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668741339302,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"schemaVersion":13}
{"_id":"zhzfD36XB0ko3ixJ","name":"Improved Mirror Shield Adjustment","type":"equipment","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/adventuring-gear/mirror.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A mirror that is custom-fitted for your shield. You gain access to the following reaction. If you use the Shield Block reaction, or gain the benefits of the Shield Block reaction with this shield in response to a critical hit from an attack, this adjustment is broken and you cannot benefit from it until it has been repaired as part of a successful Repair action on the shield.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong>&nbsp;<span class=\"pf2-icon\">r </span>envision<span class=\"pf2-icon\">;&nbsp;</span><strong>Frequency</strong> once per minute; <strong>Trigger</strong> You are targeted by an effect with the visual trait; <strong>Effect</strong> You&nbsp;gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your AC or saving throw against the triggering effect. Regardless of whether you are affected by the triggering effect, you may attempt to redirect the effect at a target within 30 feet. If the effect requires a saving throw, the target must attempt the same saving throw. If it requires an attack roll, attempt a shield attack roll to determine whether it hits.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[everything-shields.everything-shields-effects.shNds8nxBjEl4QEM]{Effect: Improved Mirror}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Everything Shields"},"traits":{"value":["adjustment"],"rarity":"uncommon","custom":"","otherTags":[]},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.93,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2025-11-10T15:51:44.920Z","version":{"schema":0.93,"foundry":"13","system":"6.0.0"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":1000}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","invested":null,"handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":"","negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/adventuring_gear.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"applied-to-shield"},"level":{"value":10}},"ownership":{"default":0,"4mqS4QLqshw8WhsN":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.4","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668741328935,"lastModifiedBy":"XyQNEFY9gmTDIpSd"},"schemaVersion":13}
